doc.after: An aircraft canopy is the transparent enclosure over the cockpit of some types of aircraft The function of the canopy is to provide a weatherproof and reasonably quiet environment for the aircraft s occupants The canopy will be as aerodynamically shaped as possible to minimize aerodynamic drag
